With over 10 years of experience in customizing open-source platforms like Dolibarr, WordPress, OpenCart and Shopify, I now specialize in building powerful and practical workflow automations and AI agents using n8n.

Whether you're looking to save time, streamline operations, or integrate AI into your business processes, I create ready-to-use n8n templates designed to make automation easy.

Based in Birmingham, UK
